data.name: Guacamole Nachos
data.quickTastyDescription: Crispy tortilla chips topped with creamy guacamole, melted cheese, and fresh toppings for a delicious snack!
detailedCookingInstructions: Spread the tortilla chips evenly on a baking sheet.
Sprinkle the shredded cheese generously over the chips.
Bake in the oven for about 5 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.
Remove from the oven and top each nacho with a dollop of guacamole.
Add optional toppings like sour cream, sliced jalapeños, chopped cilantro, and salsa as desired.
